Author: hesitantufo
Text: I know, it's Hell. I feel like I can't resist a single impulse. But we'll get through this! It's just a matter of what route to take. I don't know what I'm doing or where to go or how to stop or how to start. But it'll be okay.

Author: cardigante
Text: I wish I had some advice but honestly I’m right there with ya, I was 4-8 lbs lighter than I currently am before I started all this bull and no matter how hard I try I can’t get back to where I was before I even had this disorder UGH. Every few pounds I lose control again and binge back to where I was. What happened to my self controollll
